OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sun 1 Mar to Tue 10 Mar
OL,6,FChangeable conditions are expected,
OL,7,Fwith Atlantic frontal systems
OL,8,Fspreading across the UK, interspersed
OL,9,Fwith drier and brighter interludes.
OL,10,FRainfall will typically be heaviest in
OL,11,Fthe northwest, with much less reaching
OL,12,Fsheltered eastern areas. Some parts of
OL,13,Fthe southeast may be largely fine.
OL,14,FAcross high ground in the north, some
OL,15,Fsnow is possible at times. Winds will
OL,16,Fprobably be strong at times, with a
OL,17,Frisk of gales. Temperatures are likely
OL,18,Fto be near to or slightly above
OL,19,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
